I"Ö<p>Python fstrings can be written as follows:<br />
f‚Äù{[variable]:[modifiers][width].[#decimals][format]}‚Äù</p>
<h3 id="modifiers">modifiers:</h3>
<p>The modifiers are:</p>
<ul>
  <li>+  =   include sign</li>
  <li>x&gt; = right align (x for padding)</li>
  <li>x&lt; = left align (x for padding)</li>
  <li>x^ = centre align (x for padding)</li>
  <li>, = format with comma</li>
</ul>
